------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Description
    - Hide files with prefix rootk_
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Documentation
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation instructions
    - Compile the module
      # make
    - Clean project
      # make clean
    - View the information of rootkit.ko
      # modinfo rootkit.ko
    - Load rootkit.ko
      # insmod rootkit.ko hide_pid=xxx,yyy
    - View currently loaded kernel modules in the system
      # lsmod
    - Unload mod.ko
      # rmmod mod
    - Read log messages
      # tail -f /var/log/messages
